Great starter home or awesome for empty nesters that are down sizing. Move in ready on a full basement sitting on 1.09 acres. Includes a large generator that stays along with two large storage sheds. Hurry, this won't last! Ask how you can receive up to $1500 credit by using one of our preferred lenders. Exclusions may apply.
